text: KHDD-LP (99.3 FM) is a low-power FM radio station licensed to Oklahoma City, Oklahoma, United States. The station is currently owned by Oklahoma Catholic Family Conference, Inc. ==History== The station was assigned the call sign KHDD on September 5, 2016. ==References== ==External links== * http://www.okcr.org * HDD-LP Category:Catholic radio stations HDD-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2017 Category:2017 establishments in Oklahoma
